# ChatClient with Socket.IO

### Created by [Ludwig Eriksson](https://github.com/qepsen)

### Features
- Chat function with Socket.IO 
- Enter with a username
- Message with others in different rooms 
- Send direct messages to a specific user
- Show chat history 
- Notifications when a user joins or leaves the chat

### Client startup
 When the application starts you will need to enter your username to join the general chat room and start messaging. When you join the client for the first time the '/help' command will automatically show to help you get started.  

## Available commands

# '/help'
Show all available commands
```
/help
```

# '/dm <user> <message>' 
Send a private message to a specific user.
```
/dm Calle hello friend! 
``` 

# '/join <roomname>' 
Creates or joins a chat room.
```
/join SYS25D
```

# '/history'
Showing the message history, default is set to the last 20 messages. 
```
/history
```

# '/quit' 
Clean exit from the application. 
```
/quit
```